When you finish building Fennec for Windows Mobile, you can ask &ldquo;How can I install Fennec on my Windows Mobile handset?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Where is the installer?&rdquo;
Fennec build system creates only a zip file in the path of &ldquo;objdir/mobile/dist&rdquo;.
You might install Fennec using this zip file. But, it is cumbersome. Fortunately, the Fennnec team has released Fennec for Windows Mobile as a cab install.
&ldquo;How can they make a cab installer?

